steps.content:
Example:
```javascript
const person = {
    name: 'Alice',
    age: 25
};
```

Both styles work:
```javascript
const obj = {
    "first name": "John",
    age: 20
};
```

Example showing all types:
```javascript
const product = {
    title: "Laptop",
    price: 999,
    available: true,
    tags: ["tech", "electronics"],
    details: {
        weight: 1.5,
        color: "silver"
    }
};
```

