  sayHi: function() {
    console.log('Hi!');
  }
};
```

## üîπ 2. Shorter Method Syntax
Modern JavaScript lets you write methods more cleanly:
```javascript
const dog = {
  bark() {
    console.log('Woof!');
  }
};
```

