## üîπ 3. Merging Objects
Spread also merges objects:
```javascript
const defaults = { active: true, role: 'Guest' };
const user = { name: 'Bob', role: 'Admin' };
const merged = { ...defaults, ...user };
console.log(merged); // { active: true, role: 'Admin', name: 'Bob' }
```

